Completed tests
       19.04 real         0.88 user        15.43 sys
gcc -O3 -finline-functions -fkeep-inline-functions -funroll-loops  -o mmap-=
test mmap-test.c
/usr/bin/time ./mmap-test > /dev/null
Beginning tests with file:              services

